= ActiveForm

This plugin provides a base class for making forms with ActiveRecord validations without having a database backing.  You can use ActiveForm for:

* making forms which don't needed storage, like simpel e-mail forms
* provide extra validations on existing ActiveRecord models
* make forms for composit objects


